{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.760", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.480", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt fasse ich kurz zusammen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wor\u00fcber wir hier heute eigentlich reden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden \u00fcber wichtige Akteure der Autoindustrie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eine Forschungsvereinigung gegr\u00fcndet haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im wissenschaftlichen Sinne gar keine ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittels dieser Forschungseinrichtung sollten vermeintlich wissenschaftliche Nachweise \u00fcber die Unbedenklichkeit von Stickoxiden erbracht werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.800", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche eben nicht unbedenklich sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um also zu beweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich alle Welt einschlie\u00dflich der Weltgesundheitsorganisation irrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden Tiere und Menschen in perfiden Versuchen giftigen Gasen ausgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist erb\u00e4rmlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.400", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abgesegnet wurden diese Versuche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.120", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zu reinen PR-Zwecken durchgef\u00fchrt wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.960", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von einer universit\u00e4ren Ethikkommission, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die offenbar unter Vorspiegelung falscher Tatsachen ihre Genehmigung erteilt hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.360", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachdem nun alles aufgeflogen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gaukelt uns die Autoindustrie wieder einmal gro\u00dfe Betroffenheit vor und bringt ein paar Bauernopfer aus der zweiten Reihe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist sch\u00e4big."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir reden hier \u00fcber einen Skandal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der bereits im dritten Jahr in Folge ungel\u00f6st ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.400", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ignoranz der Autoindustrie gegen\u00fcber den gesetzlich festgesetzten Grenzwerten und die Ignoranz der Bundesregierung gegen\u00fcber allen Verst\u00f6\u00dfen bis hin zu kriminellen Handlungen haben dazu gef\u00fchrt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich spitze jetzt einmal ein bisschen zu\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.040", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gesamte Bev\u00f6lkerung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.200", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "inzwischen quasi Versuchstiere in einem deutschlandweit angelegten Abgastest sind,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das finde ich unertr\u00e4glich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.160", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob wirklich Rechtsverst\u00f6\u00dfe vorliegen oder nur Gesetzesl\u00fccken genutzt wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist hier v\u00f6llig unerheblich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wirklich entscheidend ist doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.760", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass viele Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere in der N\u00e4he von stark befahrenen Stra\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seit Jahren viel mehr Abgase einatmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.720", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als zul\u00e4ssig ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.200", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie bekommen Asthma, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Krebs und Herz-Kreislauf-Erkrankungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn also die Autoindustrie seit Jahren die gesetzlich geregelten Abgasgrenzwerte bewusst \u00fcberschreitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.880", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Menschen also bewusst diesen Risiken aussetzt und sie dabei nicht nur v\u00f6llig im Unklaren dar\u00fcber l\u00e4sst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie auch noch permanent bel\u00fcgt und t\u00e4uscht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das in meinen Augen strafbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und damit muss endlich Schluss sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.200", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.280", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die politische Verantwortung f\u00fcr diese nicht abrei\u00dfen wollende Kette von Skandalen tr\u00e4gt eindeutig eine abgewirtschaftete Bundesregierung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.160", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Umweltministerin Hendricks, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das Thema Luftreinhaltung irgendwie verschlafen hat,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.000", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein nicht mehr amtierender Verkehrsminister Dobrindt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der bayerischen Hirngespinsten hinterherl\u00e4uft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und schlie\u00dflich eine Bundeskanzlerin Merkel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Interessen der Autoindustrie offenbar \u00fcber alles stellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.360", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.600", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen endlich einen gesetzlichen Rahmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6ren Sie auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.080", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der Autoindustrie zu kuscheln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.320", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ziehen Sie die notwendigen Schlussfolgerungen aus dieser Never-ending Story!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6rt zuallererst die gesetzliche Verpflichtung der Autoindustrie zur fl\u00e4chendeckenden Nachr\u00fcstung mit SCR-Systemen in allen 7 bis 8\u00a0Millionen betroffenen Fahrzeugen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.040", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur so kann relativ schnell eine effektive Senkung der Stickoxidwerte \u00fcberhaupt erreicht werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und leiten Sie endlich Strafzahlungen f\u00fcr die Autoindustrie ein! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.160", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie kann es sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Autoindustrie seit Jahren Autos verkauft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die viel mehr Schadstoffe aussto\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als in ihren Hochglanzbrosch\u00fcren und bei der Zulassung angegeben worden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der ganze Vorgang insgesamt straffrei bleibt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcberlegen Sie doch einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was f\u00fcr ein Signal Sie damit senden! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen doch damit: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.680", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Autoindustrie steht \u00fcber dem Gesetz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gesetze gelten f\u00fcr normale Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht f\u00fcr die deutsche Autoindustrie."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.840", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die darf selbst entscheiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.640", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wann sie welches Fehlverhalten einr\u00e4umt und wann sie gedenkt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch nur freiwillig\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.280", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abhilfe zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem Ganzen die Krone setzt noch die Tatsache auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.600", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Autoindustrie gerade wieder kr\u00e4ftig verdient, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unter anderem mit ihren eigenen Betr\u00fcgereien."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.640", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch eine Farce."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.920", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein letzter Punkt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.720", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen k\u00f6nnten die Mittel aus Strafzahlungen sinnvoll an die Kommunen weitergeleitet werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.200", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ihre bisherige Ignoranz jetzt ausbaden m\u00fcssen und oft nicht einmal die Eigenbeteiligung aufbringen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "314.320", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Ihr neuestes Alibiprojekt \u201eSofortprogramm Saubere Luft\u201c vor Ort auch umsetzen zu k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "314.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "317.240", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Linke fordern wir Sie auf: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "317.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.560", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nehmen Sie endlich Ihre politische Verantwortung wahr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.560", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Menschen und f\u00fcr die Umwelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.560", 
   "children": [], 
